text: Yiniharu aba tapar'im agadi kiriya khanechan jaba tapar'im uninira pharkera januhuncha taki tapa'inle uniharula'i unako avasthama chadidinus. Tasartha tapa'inle uniharula'i unako halatama chadidinus kinabhane uniharu purna phohari chan, unako basasthana narka ho tyasa kriyakalapako sato juna tiniharule gardathe
